12
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,120
You savage woman,

13
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:03,560
I'll teach you a lesson!

14
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,080
Isn't the Etiquette Bureau

15
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,880
