111
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:16,880
(Lady Jun, City Lord's wife)
I heard Miss Zheng is quite the dancer.

112
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,880
Why not have her perform for us?

113
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,000
Hmm.

114
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,200
Bravo.

115
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,240
I've always heard

116
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,680
women of Yongzhou
are gentle and elegant.

117
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,880
Now that I've seen one,

118
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,200
it seems the rumors are true.

119
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,480
Thank you, Your Highness.

120
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,240
She can't even bow properly.

121
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,080
How rude!

122
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,440
Miss Zheng is from the common folk.

123
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:39,600
There's no need to be too harsh.

124
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,800
I must have this woman.

125
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,240
Who?

126
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,400
Who was that?

127
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,720
Eat more fruit and stop dreaming.

128
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:00,160
