to perform a duet with you?

131
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:07,760
Why not?

132
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:09,840
Ziqi.

133
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,040
Yes.

134
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,080
This plum is really sour.

135
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,960
What a fine rendition.

136
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:50,080
Many thanks to Princess Minmin

137
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,720
for this delightful melody.

138
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:54,240
It's Ziqi's accompaniment
that made it possible.

139
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,480
Princess has traveled a long way.

140
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,240
Ziqi.

141
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:02,600
Huh?

142
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:05,480
Make sure you fulfill
your duty as the host.

143
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,120
Yes, Father.

144
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:28,080
Sir.

145
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:28,360
Yes?

146
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,840
Bring me two jars of wine.

147
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,360
I'm sorry.

148
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,240
My wife is about to give birth
and I need to hurry back.

149
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,400
I'm sorry.

150
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,120
I can't even buy wine.

